---
interface Props {
  prefix: string;
  data?: {
    id?: string;
    title?: string;
    subtitle?: string;
    linkText?: string;
    linkUrl?: string;
  };
}
const { prefix, data = {} } = Astro.props;
const d = data ?? {};
---
<div class="space-y-4" data-section-type="featured_products" data-prefix={prefix}>
  <div>
    <label class="block text-xs font-medium text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-1">ID (锚点)</label>
    <input type="text" name="id" value={d.id ?? ''} placeholder="featured" class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-md bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 text-sm" />
  </div>
  <div>
    <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-1">Title</label>
    <input type="text" name="title" value={d.title ?? ''} class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-md bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 text-sm" />
  </div>
  <div>
    <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-1">Subtitle</label>
    <textarea name="subtitle" rows="2" class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-md bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 text-sm">{d.subtitle ?? ''}</textarea>
  </div>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2">
    <div>
      <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-1">Link Text</label>
      <input type="text" name="linkText" value={d.linkText ?? ''} class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-md bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 text-sm" />
    </div>
    <div>
      <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-1">Link URL</label>
      <input type="text" name="linkUrl" value={d.linkUrl ?? ''} class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-md bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 text-sm" />
    </div>
  </div>
  <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">产品列表本身来自 <code>src/data/product/</code>(在 Posts/Products 管理),此区块只控制展示文字和链接。</p>
</div>
